-- Italy's Berlusconi Says in Speech That `Baseless Attacks' Won't Stop Him
-- B y   J e f f r e y   D o n o v a n
-- 2010-11-04T12:27:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-04/italy-s-berlusconi-says-in-speech-that-baseless-attacks-won-t-stop-him.html
Italian Prime Minister Silvio
Berlusconi said “baseless attacks” will not stop him from
continuing to govern.  Berlusconi, whose term ends in 2013, made his remarks in a
speech in Rome today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
